    "Whether a cleaner corpus is necessarily better and whether a small amount of harmful information and low-quality data can bring benefits are questions that need to be explored in the future.",
    "Determining the optimal extent of data cleaning is also a topic for future research.",
    "Building the Ecosystem of Pre-training Corpora.",
    "Due to the rapid development of LLMs, a comprehensive ecosystem for pre-training corpora has not yet been established within the community.",
    "There is a lack of standards for data preprocessing, no systematic evaluation schemes for data, no established standards for the release of relevant data, and currently, there is no unified management and maintenance of data."
